definitions.definition: The main character , or one of the main characters, in any story , such as a literary work or drama .
A leading person in a contest ; a principal performer .
An advocate or champion of a cause or course of action .

main_definition: ( authorship ) The main character , or one of the main characters, in any story , such as a literary work or drama .
secondary_definitions: A leading person in a contest ; a principal performer .
( proscribed ) An advocate or champion of a cause or course of action .
